      • parseCsvToJson

        public static org.json.JSONObject parseCsvToJson(java.lang.String record,
                                                 java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> mappingFile)
        Convert a csv record to a JSON object. Read mapping between columns index and names from loaded mapping file.
        Parameters:
        record - String The csv line to be converted
        mappingFile - HashMap(String, String) A file that contains mapping between column indexes and names.
        Returns:
        JSONObject A json object, where keys are the columns' names from mapping file and values the columns from record.
